title: save_attachment()
brief: Save a single attachment to disk.
seealso: attachment, attachment_colour, count_attachments, attachments
version: 0.10
----

<p>This function will save the specified attachment to disk.</p>
<p>For example:</p>
<pre>
int count = <a href="/lua/count_attachments.html">count_attachments</a>();
int i = 1

while( i &lt;= count ) do
  save_attachment( i, "/tmp/attachment." .. i );
  i = i + 1
end
</pre>


